text.text: Best milk fish belly soup you can find in town

text.text: Fresh milk fish belly

originalText.text: Fresh milk fish belly

text.text:
It is also a long-established store that has been open for a long time and is very popular. Just cross the road diagonally across from Jing'an Station. The cuisine is Taiwanese and local.

1. Pan-fried milkfish belly
The most famous one is the fried milkfish maw. The golden fish maw is more delicious than the local ones in Tainan. I give it a full five stars💯

2. Braised pork rice
The taste is good and very authentic!

3. Pork rice
The braised pork is also very good, but there are no toppings. It would be better if there were more braised pork.

4. Dried bamboo shoots
Delicious, not greasy and plenty of portion

5. Fried tofu
It's a failure. It feels a little sour (not that it's broken). It would be better if it was made more porous to absorb juice.

All in all, it could be slightly improved, but it's definitely worth the money.

originalText.text:
也是一間老牌店了開很久很久人氣很旺。在景安站斜對面過馬路就到。料理為台式本地口味。

1.煎虱目魚肚
最有名的就是煎虱目魚肚，黃金色的魚肚，煎的比台南本地的還要好吃，給五顆星滿分💯

2.滷肉飯
口味不錯，很道地！

3.倥肉飯
倥肉也很不錯，不過沒有配料就是，如果多些滷肉就更好了。

4.筍乾
好吃，不油膩份量也很足

5.油豆腐
比較敗筆，感覺稍微有點酸味（不是壞掉啦），如果弄得多孔吸汁一點就更棒啦

總之稍可以改進，但絕對價超所值。

text.text:
The street store diagonally opposite the exit of Jing'an Station looks like a large snack bar with a semi-open space. As soon as you enter, someone will ask what you want to eat.

The pork rice is $70 (pork, shredded bamboo shoots, rice). The meat is very well braised. You can separate the meat without too much effort and the flavor is infused.
Blanched vegetables are $40. The taste is not too salty, but the saltiness is light, but I usually don’t eat too much, so it’s acceptable. There’s a lot of garlic.

originalText.text:
景安站出口斜對面的路面店，外觀就是大間的小吃店，空間半開放式，一進門會有人詢問要吃什麼

控肉飯$70（控肉、筍絲、飯），控肉滷的很爛了，不需要太費力就能夠分開肉，味道有滷進去。
燙青菜$40，味道不會太鹹，鹹味偏淡，但我平常吃的不重口，可以接受，蒜頭給很多。

text.text:
2024.02.11 Sun.
The food is served quickly and the waiter has a good memory. The taste is average, especially the braised pork rice is on the bland side, as are the fish skin soup and fish maw soup. But being able to have late night snacks at 11:30 pm is a small blessing.

originalText.text:
2024.02.11 Sun.
上菜速度很快，店員記憶力很好。味道中規中矩，尤其滷肉飯味道偏清淡，魚皮湯和魚肚湯也是。但晚上11:30能吃到宵夜夜晚是小確幸。

originalText.text: Ordered their Curry Mee + Curry Puff via Food Panda; missed my order without my curry puff. As for curry Mee, it is really soso.

text.text:
My wife went to get a manicure nearby and accidentally found this shop. I looked at the price and wow, there are very few Singaporean and Malaysian cuisines that are so cheap, so I came here to try it. My wife is Malaysian, so I came here to see if it tastes like home. .

We ordered curry rice, Hainanese chicken rice, and shrimp soup
Curry rice is considered normal, but there will be some broken bones in the sauce, so be careful.
Hainanese chicken rice, the chicken oil rice is very good, many people in Singapore and Malaysia do this. I think the chicken is ordinary, the side dishes are delicious, the chili attached is very good, it also has the taste of Singapore and Malaysia. In addition, the sauce section also comes with chili soy sauce, which is ok Eat chili rice!
The shrimp soup, my wife said it really has the flavor of Singapore and Malaysia and she likes it very much.
Finally, I took the curry puff home and it tasted exactly the same as in Singapore and Malaysia! It’s perfect for frying when you get home and you’re hungry 😂
There are also drinks available for internal use. Although the location is a bit crowded, the air conditioning is pretty good and I didn’t even sweat after eating.

Overall, it is a very good restaurant with exotic food⋯ Recommended for people from Singapore and Malaysia to try it🤪

originalText.text:
老婆去附近做美甲，無意間查到這間店，我看一下價格，哇，新馬料理這麼便宜的真得很少，就來試試了，我太太是馬來西亞人，來試試有沒有家鄉味。

我們點了咖喱飯，海南雞飯，鮮蝦湯
咖喱飯算正常，醬裡面會有些碎骨要小心。
海南雞飯，飯是雞油飯很讚，新馬很多這樣做，雞我覺得普通，小菜好吃，附的辣椒很讚，也是有新馬的味道，另外醬料區也有附辣椒醬油，可以啃辣椒剋飯！
鮮蝦湯，老婆說確實很有新馬味，很喜歡。
最後外帶了咖哩卜回去，和新馬味道一模一樣！很適合回家餓的時候氣炸一下吃😂
內用還有飲料可以喝，雖然位置有一點擠，但冷氣還不錯，吃完都沒有流汗。

整體是一間很不錯的異國美食⋯推薦新馬的可以來試試🤪
